<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[grill tomatoes, chilies, about 10 cm away from a hot grill until blistered, then turn, about 6m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Cool the vegetables, then coarsely chop them in a food processor with their juices]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[sautÃ© onion in oil on medium heat until brown, about 10m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Increase heat, when hot add tomato chili mixture, until it sizzles, about 5m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Add chicken stock, gently simmer until thick (but not too thick), about 15m]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Season]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Meanwhile prepare or reheat the tortillas, and fry the eggs sunny side up eggs in oil]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Place two of the tortillas on each plate, then slide the eggs on them.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Spoon the sauce over the eggs, garnish with coriander, onion, mexican cheese]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
